{"title":"All-New Roval Rapide 1 Piece Cockpit is Race Ready w/ Tons of Size Options","link":"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-roval-rapide-road-cockpit-one-piece/","date":1686239994000,"content":"<p>Roval has a new one-piece cockpit, and it’s not only fast — it comes in fifteen different stem/bar combinations. The goal for the Roval engineering team designing the new Rapide cockpit was straightforward — had to be the fastest bar Roval has ever made — easy, right? </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit box\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-box-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Roval started with the low-hanging fruit; they went to their in-house Retül fit experts and found the most aerodynamic yet comfortable shape they could offer. The team landed on an aero, light, stiff design that works well on the World Tour and local country roads. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Ronde van Vlaanderen recon with team SD Worx\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike--720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-on-bike-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Ronde van Vlaanderen recon with team SD Worx Photo: Francesco Rachello / Tornanti.cc</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Optimized Aerodynamics </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Roval Rapide Road Cockpit looks slightly different from the one-piece Roval Alpinist Cockpit. The shape is not only more aerodynamic but stiffer all around. The new cable and hose routing open port keeps a tidy appearance with an added aero advantage. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"406\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main--800x406.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit main\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main--800x406.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main--297x151.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main--120x61.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main--768x389.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-main-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Think of the Roval Rapide Road Cockpit as a robust road design, like an upgrade from the two-piece Rapide bar. The Roval Alpinist Cockpit is still the uber light road race offering. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"416\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight--800x416.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight--800x416.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight--297x155.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight--120x62.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight--768x400.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-weight-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, Roval claims the Rapide Cockpit has a higher stiffness-to-weight ratio than any two-piece system they’ve ever made. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view--800x579.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit top view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view--800x579.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view--297x215.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view--120x87.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view--768x556.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-top-view-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>One-Piece Construction</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Roval Rapide Road Cockpit is crafted from premium high-modulus carbon fiber, delivering ideal stiffness. The matte finish is perfect to match most frames and components, plus it can take a scratch.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit bolts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-bolts-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Available in Fifteen Different Size Combinations </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Usually, the downside of a one-piece cockpit is tweaking the final fit adjustments. Having a two-piece design allows bar rotation and some micro adjustability. For the Rapide Cockpit, Roval partnered with Retül fit professionals and the best riders in the world to ensure almost every rider can find their fit. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit computer mounts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-computer-mounts-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit cable port\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-cable-port-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit mounting bolts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-mounting-bolts-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Roval Rapide Cockpit is available in 15 different stem and bar combos at -6 degrees. The radius from tops to drops has been sculpted for wrist clearance, whether in or out of the saddle and is strikingly similar to the design of the Rapide II bar. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"One piece Roval Rapide Road Cockpit logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/One-piece-Roval-Rapide-Road-Cockpit-logo-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Roval Rapide Road Cockpit Details </h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Weight: 334 grams (120mm x 420mm)  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fifteen combos: 75mm to 380mm / 125mm to 440cm\n<ul>\n<li>75mm X 380mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>90mm x 380mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>100mm x 400mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>110mm x 400mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>120mm x 400mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>100mm x 420mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>110mm x 420mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>120mm x 420mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>110mm x 440mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>125mm x 440mm</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Angle: -6 Drop and Reach: 125mm x 75mm  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Material: Premium High Modulus Carbon Fiber  </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cable Routing: Internal / Electronic Compatible </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price: $600 </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out more on the <a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en/shop/equipment/bike-components/c/bikecomponents?gclid=CjwKCAjw-IWkBhBTEiwA2exyO_zyVt5QqHoZHic4p9v1UP-ST1kdXEaiFOZrAQbJwtD6ih5UY6D4ohoC7Z8QAvD_BwE#/filter:group:Wheels\" target=\"_blank\">All-New Roval Rapide Road Cockpit here</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-roval-rapide-road-cockpit-one-piece/\">All-New Roval Rapide 1 Piece Cockpit is Race Ready w/ Tons of Size Options </a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4cf1d45f3a1c05b42689a6bff4cedaf957bcf444746bd8fc268533b388f5a486","category":"Cycling"}